name: Sync to publication repo

# DISABLED
#
# Do not enable this workflow in TIBHannover/datacite-metadata-toolkit.
#
# A workflow running in this repository only receives a GITHUB_TOKEN scoped to
# this repository. It cannot push branches or open pull requests in
# TIBHannover/datacite unless a separate cross-repository token is added.
#
# The preferred no-secret design is inverted:
#
#   1. Run the sync workflow in TIBHannover/datacite.
#   2. Checkout TIBHannover/datacite-metadata-toolkit as a read-only source.
#   3. Copy source/production-namespace/{class,property,vocab,context,manifest,dist}
#      plus source/production-namespace/CHECKSUMS.sha256 into the publication repo.
#   4. Use that repository's built-in GITHUB_TOKEN to open a review PR in
#      TIBHannover/datacite.
#
# Root publication files such as .nojekyll, LICENSE, README.md, and index.html
# belong to TIBHannover/datacite and should not be overwritten by this toolkit.
